                    "children": [
                      {
                        "type": "text",
                        "text": "Blow Fire Down the Coast."
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": " A rowdy fighting song from the Clovis Concord, this ditty talks of blasting up pirate ships. Use it to encourage battle."
