                      {
                        "type": "text",
                        "text": "Drink Deep, Li'l Hummingbird."
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": " A drinking rondo from the Menagerie Coast, this song tells the tale of a young person who drinks so heavily that they awaken to find they've stowed away on a ship. Use it to encourage alertness in social situations."
